          "text": "## Deliverable\n\n**PR:** https://github.com/li-langverse/lic/pull/176  \n**Branch:** `cursor/compiler-studio-plan-loop` (pushed `82269ae`)\n\n### wave-a-7d-vectorized\n\n1. **`@vectorized` on `def`** — MIR lowering sets `MirFn.vectorized_lanes` (default **4** when `lanes` is omitted):\n\n```48:56:compiler/mir/lower.cpp\nvoid apply_fn_decorator_codegen_flags(MirFn& fn) {\n  for (const auto& d : fn.decorators) {\n    if (d.name == \"vectorized\") {\n      fn.vectorized_lanes = d.lanes > 0 ? d.lanes : 4;\n    }\n    if (d.name == \"no_vectorize\") {\n      fn.no_vectorize = true;\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n2. **E0323** — `@vectorized` + `@no_vectorize` on the same `def` is a compile error (inner `for` `@vectorized` still allowed per 7d-c).\n\n3. **G-par Lean roadmap** — expanded **P-par** row in `docs/verification/proof-corpus-roadmap.md` (disjoint from 7d SIMD work); **G-dec** / **G-par** rows updated in `provability-gaps.md`.\n\n4. **Plan YAML** — `wave-a-7d-vectorized` marked **completed** in `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-05-22-compiler-studio-plan-loop.md`.\n\n### Files changed\n\n| Area | Paths |\n|------|--------|\n| Compiler | `compiler/mir/include/li/mir.hpp`, `lower.cpp`, `mir.cpp`, `policy_module.cpp`, `lic/main.cpp`, `error_codes.*` |\n| Tests | `li-tests/decorators/vectorized_def_*.li`, `li-tests/tooling/vectorized_def_mir_smoke.sh`, `manifest.toml` |\n| Docs | `proof-corpus-roadmap.md`, `provability-gaps.md`, `fast-math-and-parallelism.md`, release notes, CHANGELOG |\n\n### Tests run\n\n```bash\n./scripts/build.sh\n./li-tests/tooling/vectorized_def_mir_smoke.sh\n./li-tests/run_all.sh decorators          # 11 passed\n./scripts/compiler-studio-plan-gates.sh # green (math_linalg, goldens, tier-1 verify, 2f Lean)\n```\n\n`LI_MIR_DECOR_FLAGS=1 lic verify …` prints `mir_decor fn=dot4 vectorized_lanes=4` for the smoke check."
